{"word":"G5032 - τάχιον - táchion - takh'-ee-on - Out","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">τάχιον</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">táchion</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">takh'-ee-on</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Out</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"சீக்கிரமாய் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"more swiftly, more quickly"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Neuter singular of the comparative of <a href=\"#/G5036 - ταχύς - tachýs - takh-oos'/5036\">G5036</a> (as adverb); <i>more swiftly</i>, that is, (in manner) <i>more rapidly</i>, or (in time) <i>more speedily:</i> - out [run], quickly, shortly, sooner.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}